    "Individual guidelines are listed in the next section.",
    "Key regulatory bodies emphasize the necessity of transparency, accountability, and ethical use and that AI cannot fulfill authorship criteria due to its inability to declare conflicts of interest, manage publication rights, or handle licensing agreements.",
